{
  "text": "Experiments on both SVM and WSVM were conducted with Libsvm, which was developed by professor Lin [CITATION_1] . For each classification problem, we generate a total of 1000 data points and for cross validation purposes, 90% of the data was used for training and the rest 10% was used for testing.",
